{"tid":2109071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美趨強硬「火藥桶」一觸即發","createTime":"2020-07-15T03:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T03:38:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16a6dfca7b38efd0440c27110e408a6c54dd192d","tid":2109071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/O72SUNRSCADOZNBRZN3X4H66OY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FO72SUNRSCADOZNBRZN3X4H66OY%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=02128a25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FO72SUNRSCADOZNBRZN3X4H66OY%2F&h=b7081654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/O72SUNRSCADOZNBRZN3X4H66OY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美趨強硬「火藥桶」一觸即發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a5la2GMkD1rL-z8iE-lklP9h1aA=/706x389/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGWPEMCRDCRCHQGARADLWUTOMA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa5la2GMkD1rL-z8iE-lklP9h1aA%3D%2F706x389%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGWPEMCRDCRCHQGARADLWUTOMA.gif&h=604e043b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尼米茲號與列根號月初在南海演練，對華示威。<br />\n(motherlode)<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】美國一反既往立場，就南海問題發表強硬聲明，反對北京對南海主權主張。中外輿論及專家皆認為，此標誌着美國對南海不再持「中立」立場。美戰艦軍機今後將在南海有更多威懾中方舉動，甚至不排除中美在南海兵戎相見或局部衝突可能。<br />\n<br />\n美國戰略與國際研究中心中國問題專家葛來儀認為，新立場「將使美國能更有力回擊中國對該區域其他主權聲索國的騷擾」，為這些弱小國家「出頭」抗中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對華宣示主權直接挑戰<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國際法庭裁「九段線」違法<br />\n<br />\n彭博社稱，美做法是對中共在南海宣示控制權的直接挑戰。《華爾街日報。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中共空軍上將劉亞洲的胞弟、全美中國研究聯合會長劉亞偉指，美過往對南海立場是「主權問題不選邊，只關心航行自由」。現。。。。。。。"}]}